{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, much effort is required to ensure the high quality of the additional data.",
    "In practice, there may be cases where the data sources contain counterfactual or even false information that should be eliminated.",
    "Therefore, organizations need to allocate more resources and build new capabilities, such as MLOps capabilities, to implement RAG-based systems.",
    "In addition to data management issues, the underlying data inevitably presents new challenges in terms of unwanted bias effects.",
    "This is because organizations have a new way of adding data to the AI infrastructure via a vector database."
  ]
}